data.meta_description: Oct 5, 2023 - [Guadalupe Victoria Yoli Raymond]  Born in San Pedrito, Santiago, Cuba. Anything that i may add, or, by omission subtract about La Lupe would pale in comparison to what men of such diverse intellectual leanings as Jean-Paul Sartre and Pablo Picasso said about her, calling her act, "Genius".  Much like her contemporary Celia Cruz her father insisted that she study for a profession, so she graduated from the University of Havana with a teacher's certificate. A composite of: Piaf, Kitt, Joplin. See more ideas about la lupe, guadalupe victoria, celia cruz.
